spanGrp.span: Our people are a bit serious.
ee bizm halh ee biräz šeidır serioznidır
That is because they have a difficult history.
aa sora aa onučun ki onnar onnarın var mm belä onučun ki onnarın var čätın istoriasi aa
i onnar ee heč istämerlär ki ee görsädälär biše
They want to live by themselves.
onnar istierlär ki yašarlar ee gändi gändınä
But people who live here like for everyone to know everything about them.
hama burda ki yašerlar halh onnar isterlär ki mm onnarın yašamasi häp adamlar bülä
And to show how good they are.
ee i görä ki onnar ee yaxši halhtırlar
But our people don’t need such kind of things.
hama bizım halh bizım halha belä išlär lazımdägıl
